/* Factory Management System Custom Styles - Light Theme */

/* PROFESSIONAL TYPOGRAPHY STANDARDS
   Following industry best practices for professional UI/UX:
   - Body text: 16px (1rem) - Standard readable size
   - Form inputs/labels: 16px (1rem) - Consistent with body
   - Buttons: 16px (1rem) - Easily readable
   - Navigation: 16px (1rem) - Professional navigation standard
   - Small notes/captions: 12-13px (0.75-0.8125rem) - Secondary text
   - Headings: 20-32px (1.25-2rem) - Proper hierarchy
